Interface Primitive

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Primitive
extends PrimitivePower
    A numeric primitive expression, e.g., a symbolic constant of numeric type, an array read expression of numeric type, or a tuple read expression of numeric type. This is a marker interface.
